{"tid":371350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳第三世界停車場死左好多人，堅定流?","createTime":"2017-08-23T15:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T18:05:54.000Z","uid":5195,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97d659ecd337fd926f748f1ad92fd447b4165c2b","tid":371350,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:47:56.000Z","msg":"明天新聞 希望澳門政府老實交代死亡人數<br />\n（本人有朋友做消防，已得知死亡人數，但基於不想交代太多，更不想對死者不敬，希望政府部門！從實報導！）<br />\n更新消息（是朋友發給我的 已幫他祈禱 但有消息指已經有部分人士死亡並被抬出 部份死於車內）<br />\n點算丫！！重無人既朋友係停車場（影片非停車場）！ 但澳門兩個地下停車場 都水浸了。大家可以想像 由地庫浸到負四層。<br />\n真心希望佢地平安無事。<br />\n為佢地同無能既澳門政府祈禱。真心好難聽講句，澳門政府廢過中央<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21032845_1472522949470001_4848184171508544531_n.jpg?oh=3e1bde7769a0565b17979aab3307af6c&amp;oe=5A24991D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21032845_1472522949470001_4848184171508544531_n.jpg%3Foh%3D3e1bde7769a0565b17979aab3307af6c%26oe%3D5A24991D&h=00c56981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20953722_1842712859088629_1542268288228783247_n.jpg?oh=4a761f0fea22bc7766917d714d4c22a3&amp;oe=5A21548B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20953722_1842712859088629_1542268288228783247_n.jpg%3Foh%3D4a761f0fea22bc7766917d714d4c22a3%26oe%3D5A21548B&h=9dd54b76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f629a08564ce82dc6b2fa7be8b0f7f1789f83dae","tid":371350,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf9b1caad15c046baa5927221a3b9046b1c3955","tid":371350,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"似真, 毒果出左"},{"pid":"d7d893c676e76804a8af309a1d913e9729ebbe8b","tid":371350,"uid":54278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15: